        }
        <section class="getting-started">
            <h3 class="cushycms">Getting Started</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-GettingStarted-Q1" class="cushycms">How do I hire a service provider?</a></li>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-GettingStarted-Q2" class="cushycms">How do I become a provider?</a></li>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-GettingStarted-Q3" class="cushycms">What information do I need?</a></li>
            </ol>
            <a href="#FAQs-GettingStarted" class="more cushycms">View more</a>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h3 class="cushycms">Scheduling Services</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-SchedulingServices-Q1" class="cushycms">Do I need to choose alternate times?</a></li>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-SchedulingServices-Q2" class="cushycms">When will my booking be confirmed?</a></li>
                <li><a href="#FAQs-SchedulingServices-Q3" class="cushycms">Why do I pay upfront?</a></li>
            </ol>
            <a href="#FAQs-SchedulingServices" class="more cushycms">View more</a>
